line_2: The doctrines warpt to what they never meant.
Some foe to his upright intent

line_1: Had that calm look which seem'd to all assent,
line_2: And that complacent speech which nothing meant:

line_1: To cheat themselves and gain the world's assent
line_2: And of all arts sagacious dupes invent

line_1: To cheat themselves and gain the world's assent
line_2: The worst is scripture warp'd from it's intent.
